        [
          "Staff Generated History"
        ],
        [
          "You were part of the punk movment in the 1970's in london. You felt the rage of the people though you, but that rage needed directon and leadership, Soon you were the part of a biker gang. One night you saw a woman in a fur coat walking down a dark alley. Your gang attcked her planing to rob her. It did not take long for the \"helpless\" woman to have killed most of the members of your gang. As they screamed asking you to help them, your soon to be sire, dominated you to watch them be ripped apart. Your sire embraced you right there, and brought you in the the sect by feeding on your own friends. A few years later you were a proven member. You attacked the pawns of Mithris, and kept a wide berth from his scourge. In 1990, a plan was brought up to you, a plan to kill the toreador primagion of london. It was a plan most people said could not be done. but you were not most people. As you succeeded you were brought in to the Black Hand. You have spent the interving years working as the fist of the regent, killing who needed to be killed and being their voice in the wars of the sect.  Your Pack, the Night Dragons, is a column of Black Hand killers.  Keep this a secret from all outside the hand.  Your Allied Pack, Cardine Scorso, is also in San Diego."
